**Theorem (matrix-vector backward error)**
For $A âˆˆ â„^{m Ã— n}$ and $ğ± âˆˆ â„^n$ we have
$$
{\rm mul}(A, ğ±) = (A + Î´A) ğ±
$$
where
$$
